title: SEO For WordPress [Beginners]: #1 Step-by-Step SEO System
description:
Description

“Introducing My Simple Step-by-Step SEO System For WordPress!””The No Filler, No Fluff, Step-by-Step SEO Game Plan Designed to Take You From Zero SEO Knowledge to The First Page of Google in 60-90 Days!”Everybody knows that getting to the first page of the search engines is going to bring them more traffic, more prospects, and ultimately more profits.My simple SEO blueprint is your opportunity to get those results without spending a fortune on consultants, or being frustrated with the complexity of SEO.

Who is the target audience?

    This “SEO For WordPress” course is meant for small business owners and bloggers that want to get on the first page of Google, Yahoo, and Bing.
    This SEO course is designed for beginner and intermediate WordPress users. No technical or HTML coding knowledge is required.
    This course is probably not for you if you’re a web developer, HTML coder, or an SEO consultant.

Requirements

    Basic computer skills
    Familiar with WordPress
